=========
 TRACLOG 
=========
| 

about
-----
| 

:author:  Bart Thate <bthate@gmail.com>
:contact: IRCNET/#dunkbots
:distribution: core
:license: Public Domain
 
| 

description
-----------
| 

log irc channels in trac format

| 

  log irc channels in trac format (0.10.4) 

| 

commands
--------
| 

1) *traclog-cfg*

    :description: plugin configuration

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !traclog-cfg
        <output> options: channels=[] .. version="GOZERBOT 0.9"


2) *traclog-cfgsave*

    :description: save plugin configuration

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !traclog-cfgsave
        <output> config saved


3) *traclog-off*

    :description: disable traclog on <channel> or the channel the commands is given in

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !traclog-off
        <output> traclog is not enabled in (gozerdata,#test)



    ::

        <user> !traclog-off #dunkbots
        <output> traclog is not enabled in (gozerdata,#test)


4) *traclog-on*

    :description: enable  traclog on <channel> or the channel the commands is given in

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !traclog-on
        <output> traclog enabled on (gozerdata,#test)



    ::

        <user> !traclog-on #dunkbots
        <output> traclog enabled on (gozerdata,#test)


